markdownRemark.html: I hope you will find time to read it, Mary, and that we can discuss it sometime. It is a very curious ranking and definition of the disciplines, in which Astrology becomes an umbrella for all the earth and sky-related sciences. Perhaps you can identify a source for this strange umbrella!
